{
  "2141520": {
    "name": "Survivor Mercs",
    "steam_appid": 2141520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>对抗机械暴政</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">肉鸽玩法。机械狂潮。小队建设。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 M.E.G.A. 集团的私人机器人军队威胁下，人类最后的希望，是一群报名当雇佣兵的武装疯子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而领导他们的最佳人选？当然是一个拥有随机特质的一次性克隆人。欢迎上岗，指挥官。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领这支经费不足却野心勃勃的队伍踏上战场，打造成能横扫邪恶亿万富翁的末日战争机器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜算渺茫？无所谓！这场仗打的不是荣耀，而是为了战利品！  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>运气也是实力的一种！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位指挥官在创建时都会随机生成一组特性。你能带领一位鹰眼敏锐、狡猾的渗透者取得胜利吗？还是会独自迎战敌人，以夜行性贪婪的‘一人成军’之姿出击？又或者选择一个聪明绝顶的吸血忍者呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种特性组合都会带来独特的挑战、游戏机制和令人惊喜的协同效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备你最钟爱的武器，释放混乱吧！不过首先，你需要一支队伍： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>精英小队,集结!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一支身经百战的战士阵容中组建你的佣兵小队。每位佣兵都配备专属武器和个人战术，应对机器人大军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤你的佣兵克隆增援，为他们选择最适合行动的专精路线，并通过高科技装备提升战斗力，打造一支毁天灭地、横扫敌群的超级小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>唯利弑图!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在程序生成的多阶段地图上，发起针对M.E.G.A.集团及其子公司的作战行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺取目标以召唤增援，完成任务，掠夺珍贵战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快准狠！时间紧迫——战场上每过一分钟，敌人就会变得更强更多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>以退为进!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往撤离点并坚守阵地，直到直升机带你进入下一个阶段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奋力战斗、设法生存，挑战独特又庞大的Boss与其爪牙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但务必小心——胜者全得，败者全失！一旦阵亡，战利品也将化为乌有；只有活着才能带回战利品，卷土重来，愈战愈强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>欲善其事, 先利其器 - 升级基地!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投资你的战利品以雇佣新佣兵、购买新装备、拓建你的基地并进行永久升级，或为指挥官克隆体研发新特性和武器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>独一无二的行动!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战术技能指挥你的佣兵，或在战斗中亲自上阵——每位指挥官克隆体与配置都提供独特的战术选择与战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断尝试，找出最适合应对M.E.G.A.公司挑战的最佳小队配置。每一次战斗体验都独一无二！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.poster.avif?t=1768516879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.webm?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.mp4?t=1768516879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>组队出击!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时畅快加入或退出本地合作，最多4位好友将操控你的佣兵，在你这位荣耀指挥官的带领下并肩作战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制一名由3种随机特性生成的指挥官克隆体，拥有超过15,000种独特组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过主动控制武器及各种主动和被动技能来指挥你的小队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从大量具有独特技能树和专长的雇佣兵中组建你的队伍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从数十种装备中进行选择，改进和增强你的队伍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在程序生成的地图上执行任务，每张地图拥有不同的任务参数、难度和独特头目。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成剧情任务，结识你的佣兵，扩充武器库，并揭穿 M.E.G.A.集团头目的秘密计划。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拓建你的基地，在行动中搜刮的战利品可用来建造和升级房间，解锁更多战术选择与永久加成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友组队开启沙发合作，一同横扫战场——或通过 Steam Remote Play Together 联手作战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全支持手柄及键盘/鼠标输入。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过Twitch集成直播游戏，让观众来决定你的命运。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在SteamDeck上游玩，已完全兼容 </p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 法语, 意大利语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
